BT /F2 13.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 614.58 Tm (2.1 What It Is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 596.42 Tm (Amazon EC2 is a virtual machine service. You get compute instances with CPU, memory,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 582.56 Tm (network, and attached storage. You manage the OS, patching, runtime, scaling logic, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 568.70 Tm (usually the application lifecycle.) Tj ET
