BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 485.10 Tm (- you need specific agents, kernels, drivers, or custom networking behavior) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 471.24 Tm (- you want predictable long-running servers) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 457.38 Tm (- you are running self-managed databases, build agents, or stateful middleware) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 443.52 Tm (Avoid defaulting to EC2 when the team actually wants less operational overhead.) Tj ET
