BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 734.56 Tm (The team might do:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 718.70 Tm (- React build served by Nginx) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 704.84 Tm (- Spring Boot JAR running as a systemd service) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 690.98 Tm (- both hosted on one or more EC2 instances) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 677.12 Tm (- ALB in front) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 663.26 Tm (This works. It is not elegant, but it works.) Tj ET
