BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 577.66 Tm (- "Why does prod behave differently from staging?") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 563.80 Tm (- "Why are we patching machines manually?") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 549.94 Tm (- "Why did this deployment break one node but not the others?") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 536.08 Tm (At this point, the team wants:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 520.22 Tm (- immutable deployments) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 506.36 Tm (- predictable runtime packaging) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 492.50 Tm (- easier rollback) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 478.64 Tm (- easier autoscaling) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 464.78 Tm (- less server-level operational work) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 450.92 Tm (That usually leads to ECS.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 435.06 Tm (Why?) Tj ET
