BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 363.76 Tm (- lower operational overhead than Kubernetes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 349.90 Tm (Now the team runs:) Tj ET
