BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 321.88 Tm (Check in this order:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 302.02 Tm ([text]) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 290.14 Tm (1. Is the RDS in the same VPC as the backend?) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 278.26 Tm (2. Is the backend's security group allowed outbound to port 5432?) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 266.38 Tm (3. Is the RDS security group allowing inbound from the backend's security group?) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 254.50 Tm (4. Is the backend using the correct RDS endpoint hostname?) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 242.62 Tm (5. Are the database credentials correct?) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 230.74 Tm (6. Are they in the same \(or peered\) subnets?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 212.86 Tm (90% of the time it is a security group misconfiguration.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 191.00 Tm (12.2 "My backend cannot call external APIs") Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 168.84 Tm ([text]) Tj ET
