BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 145.08 Tm (2. Is there a NAT Gateway in a public subnet?) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 133.20 Tm (3. Does the private subnet's route table have:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 121.32 Tm (     0.0.0.0/0 -> NAT Gateway?) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 109.44 Tm (4. Does the backend's security group allow outbound on port 443?) Tj ET
