BT /F2 18.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 641.08 Tm (App's Data Actually Lives) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 615.32 Tm (Source file: AWS-07-Storage-Story-Mode.md) Tj ET
