BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 415.76 Tm (business truth remains in RDS, Aurora, or DynamoDB. If the cache is lost,) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 403.88 Tm (the app should slow down temporarily, not lose correctness permanently.") Tj ET
