BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 175.52 Tm (Think of it as four layers:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 155.66 Tm ([text]) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 143.78 Tm (Layer 1: IAM            -> controls what AWS resources your code can touch) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 131.90 Tm (Layer 2: Network        -> controls what traffic can flow where) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 120.02 Tm (Layer 3: Secrets + Encryption -> protects data at rest and in transit) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 108.14 Tm (Layer 4: App Auth       -> controls who your end users are and what they can do) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 90.26 Tm (Each layer is independent. You need all four.) Tj ET
