BT /F2 15.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 338.52 Tm (5. Who Can Call AWS Services - IAM) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 316.72 Tm (This is the most fundamental security concept on AWS.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 294.86 Tm (5.1 The Problem) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 276.70 Tm (Your Spring Boot app needs to:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 260.84 Tm (- read secrets from Secrets Manager) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 246.98 Tm (- upload files to S3) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 233.12 Tm (- send messages to SQS) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 64.00 219.26 Tm (- pull images from ECR) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 205.40 Tm (How does AWS know your app is allowed to do these things?) Tj ET
BT /F2 13.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 183.54 Tm (5.2 Real-Life Analogy) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 161.38 Tm ([text]) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 149.50 Tm (IAM is like a company badge system.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 137.62 Tm () Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 125.74 Tm (Every employee \(user\) and every robot \(service/application\) gets a badge.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 113.86 Tm (The badge says what doors they can open and what rooms they can enter.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 101.98 Tm () Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 90.10 Tm (Without a badge, you cannot do anything.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 78.22 Tm (With a badge scoped to "Floor 3 only," you cannot reach Floor 5.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 479.00 24.00 Tm (Page 114 of 147) Tj ET
endstream
