BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 416.74 Tm (  Simple. Works for most apps.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 404.86 Tm () Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 392.98 Tm (Attribute-Based \(ABAC\):) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 381.10 Tm (  "User can access resource if user.department == resource.department) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 369.22 Tm (   AND user.clearance >= resource.sensitivityLevel") Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 357.34 Tm (  More flexible. More complex. Used in enterprise/compliance scenarios.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 339.46 Tm (For most Spring Boot apps, RBAC is enough.) Tj ET
