BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 575.26 Tm (  The Docker image should contain zero secrets.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 551.38 Tm (12.2 "We gave the backend AdministratorAccess") Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 529.22 Tm ([text]) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 517.34 Tm (Problem:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 505.46 Tm (  If the app is compromised, the attacker owns your entire AWS account.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 493.58 Tm () Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 481.70 Tm (Fix:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 469.82 Tm (  Scope IAM role to exact actions and resources needed.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 457.94 Tm (  s3:GetObject on one bucket = s3:* on *.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 434.06 Tm (12.3 "We put RDS in a public subnet") Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 411.90 Tm ([text]) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 400.02 Tm (Problem:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 388.14 Tm (  One security group mistake = database exposed to the internet.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 376.26 Tm () Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 364.38 Tm (Fix:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 352.50 Tm (  RDS in private subnet. Always.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 340.62 Tm (  Security group allows only backend security group on port 5432.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 316.74 Tm (12.4 "We hardcoded AWS access keys in the app") Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 294.58 Tm ([text]) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 282.70 Tm (Problem:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 270.82 Tm (  Keys in code get committed to Git.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 258.94 Tm (  Keys in environment files get logged.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 247.06 Tm (  Rotation becomes manual and error-prone.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 235.18 Tm () Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 223.30 Tm (Fix:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 211.42 Tm (  Use IAM roles. The AWS SDK finds credentials automatically.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 199.54 Tm (  Zero access keys in application code, config, or Docker images.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 46.00 175.66 Tm (12.5 "We disabled HTTPS because it was hard to set up") Tj ET
