BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 105.98 Tm (Fix:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 94.10 Tm (  ACM provides free TLS certificates.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 82.22 Tm (  ALB handles TLS termination with one configuration.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 70.34 Tm (  There is no valid reason to skip HTTPS in production.) Tj ET
