BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 81.80 Tm (the ALB terminates HTTPS using a free ACM certificate. Backend-to-RDS ) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 69.92 Tm (connections enforce TLS. S3 access via the SDK uses HTTPS by default. ) Tj ET
